"n.教条，信条 【考】 dogma : iconoclast / convention : maverick(攻击传统观念的人不 相信教条/想法与众不 同的人不相信传统)反义词：heresy(异端 邪说) n. 教条(由教堂以权威的方式提出与道德信仰有关的, 被一帮人绝对相信的东西) 【记】dog顽强的狗, 顽强的坚持dog的mama－教条 【参】dogmatic(adj 教条的; 独断的) = doctrinal = dictatorialdogmatism(n 教条主义; 武断) 【类】dogma: iconoclast = convention: maverick攻击传统观念的人不信教条 = 想法与众不同的人不信传统 【反】heresy(n 异端邪说) 【记】doctor 博士,相信教条的 【相关】doctrine 教条, 学说, diploma 文凭 dogma (n.)  c.1600 (in plural dogmata), from Latin dogma ""philosophical tenet,"" from Greek dogma (genitive dogmatos) ""opinion, tenet,"" literally ""that which one thinks is true,"" from dokein ""to seem good, think"" (see decent). Treated in 17c.-18c. as a Greek word in English."
